open the file in mkvmerge gui ..then deselect the audio file ..english audio file [from tracks,chapters and tags]..
click on start muxing.. and the play output file on tv.

@vginside123 
for changing the default audio..open the file in mkvmerge gui and click on the audio file which u want to make it default..
then on general track options.. default track flag click on yes for the audio u want to make default and no for the other file.
